的病人数下降。 但在呼吸内科，风暴眼中的风暴眼，所有医院收治新冠重症病人都会集中这个楼层进行抢救和处置，仍然是吃劲的时候。 早上 8 点，53 岁的呼吸科主任饶建亚正准备去查房。51 张病床，6 位医生，11 位护士，连轴转了一个多月，几乎全阳了，她也没能坚持住。 饶主任告诉我，呼吸内科科室大多是危重病人。12 月中旬，科室的人全部收满了，「几乎是我一人跑全院会诊」「脑子里还没有过年的概念」。 基层与返乡潮赛跑，春运期间一线状况如何？还面临哪些困难？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-b7c54d467c1f94879ddb1774e2dfc643_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579482965"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik4TmoOKcqqJWEAMaCDkxMDU1NjkwIMmhoJ4GMAU4zgJAF3IJNTc5NDgyOTY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1674493686.4611554", "card_id": "Q_580059261", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 72}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人到中年，赚钱重要还是身体重要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580059261"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ik4TmoOKcqqJWEAMaCDkxMTgzNzc0IMfPtJ4GMAA4WkAYcgk1ODAwNTkyNjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1674493686.4616256", "card_id": "Q_427129273", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 271}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "说说你心中的 NBA 的历史前十？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picd.zhimg.com/80/v2-ba962eef85566de80a84dd6c8bda8117_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/427129273"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik4TmoOKcqqJWEAMaCDU3MTk2ODczIIGaz/wFMAE4twJAGXIJNDI3MTI5MjczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type":